          Schedule a Demo
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+15615624300" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-transparent text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-all border-2 border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
